    <item>
      <title>特朗普竞选团队称，特朗普曾被告知“具体”的伊朗暗杀阴谋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/trump-told-of-specific-iran-assassination-plot-campaign-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普的竞选团队在一份声明中表示，拜登政府官员周二向特朗普介绍了“伊朗发出的暗杀他的真实而具体的威胁”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/trump-told-of-specific-iran-assassination-plot-campaign-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 01:24:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗总统称预计将举行核协议会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/iran-president-says-he-expects-to-hold-meeting-on-nuclear-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗总统马苏德·佩泽什基安表示，在与法国领导人埃马纽埃尔·马克龙举行“积极”会谈后，双方正计划讨论搁置多年的核协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/iran-president-says-he-expects-to-hold-meeting-on-nuclear-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:49:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BT：新加坡总检察长将很快对房地产大亨王某做出决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/singapore-agc-to-take-decision-on-property-tycoon-ong-soon-bt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《商业时报》报道，新加坡前交通部长 S. Iswaran 周二承认受贿和妨碍司法公正的指控后，新加坡总检察长办公室将“很快”对房地产大亨王明成做出裁决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/singapore-agc-to-take-decision-on-property-tycoon-ong-soon-bt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:20:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国第一夫人会见美国学生，努力改善两国关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/xi-s-wife-meets-us-students-in-effort-to-improve-relations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平的夫人彭丽媛会见了一批来访的美国学生——强调了北京修复与美国关系的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/xi-s-wife-meets-us-students-in-effort-to-improve-relations</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:15:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华盛顿州长候选人弗格森为资本利得税辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/washington-governor-candidate-ferguson-defends-capital-gains-tax</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿州州长候选人鲍勃·弗格森为该州的资本利得税辩护，强调其在资助教育方面发挥的重要作用，而共和党支持的投票倡议则试图废除该税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/washington-governor-candidate-ferguson-defends-capital-gains-tax</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:00:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 向白宫推介前所未有的数据中心建设</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/openai-pitched-white-house-on-unprecedented-data-center-buildout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI 向拜登政府强调了对大型数据中心的需求，每个数据中心所用的电量可能相当于整个城市，并称这种前所未有的扩张是开发更先进的人工智能模型和与中国竞争的必要条件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/openai-pitched-white-house-on-unprecedented-data-center-buildout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 23:45:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普枪手嫌疑人被指控企图暗杀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/suspected-trump-gunman-charged-with-attempted-assassination</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名男子被发现藏身于唐纳德·特朗普高尔夫球场的灌木丛中，手持一支上了膛的步枪，该男子因企图暗杀这位前总统而被起诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/suspected-trump-gunman-charged-with-attempted-assassination</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 23:36:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国会议暴露分歧 伊朗总统向西方发起挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/iran-s-new-leader-takes-un-stage-as-israel-hezbollah-war-spreads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗新总统周二首次在联合国大会上发表全球演讲，他警告以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击“不能不予以回应”，并敦促西方国家重返核协议并解除对伊朗伊斯兰共和国的制裁，从而成功主导了当天的发言。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/iran-s-new-leader-takes-un-stage-as-israel-hezbollah-war-spreads</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 18:47:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击黎巴嫩真主党 造成 500 多人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/israel-s-bombing-of-hezbollah-targets-kills-hundreds-in-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列对真主党目标进行了更多空袭，这是自 2006 年双方爆发灾难性战争以来，以色列对黎巴嫩实施的最严重、伤亡最惨重的轰炸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/israel-s-bombing-of-hezbollah-targets-kills-hundreds-in-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 09:05:18 GMT</pubDate>
